{"title":"瞩目国旗","authors":["高洪波"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":12,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞩目国旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为澳门回归作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高洪波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从简陋的拱北海关走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过国旗，走过另一种旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两面旗帜在风中絮语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用风的语言鸟的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交流着四百年的复杂情感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞩目国旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这覆盖着中国辽阔版图的大纛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近在咫尺澳门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却温暖不住你的身躯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今另一种旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"另一种航海而来驭炮而来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经强悍过的旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经驯服地降落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞩目国旗的刹那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看到了圆满、美丽和辉煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"零丁洋上的波涛声里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此拥有了欢乐和暖意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞩目国旗"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}